{"tid":1102779,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想想別人@2014","createTime":"2019-04-12T03:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T03:17:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"009aa49a54d2c85d7d91a647a937f0fd33d3c183","tid":1102779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190412/20654016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20654016&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctztT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=ceacf3d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20654016&h=5b0c66bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190412/20654016</a><br />\n<br />\n想想別人@2014 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190412/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190412%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=3c323071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n當你做早餐時想想別人，別忘記獅子山上的黃幡。<br />\n<br />\n當你與全世界閒到發慌那個人爭論時，別忘記120萬堅守和平爭取真普選的人。<br />\n<br />\n當你交利得稅時想想別人，那些只能等住逃犯條例移送到殘酷地方的人。<br />\n<br />\n當你回到家裏，想想牢獄中，曾經79天住在帳篷的人。<br />\n<br />\n當你入睡前分享了朋友極光打卡照片時想想別人，那些在星空下被剝奪日常的人。<br />\n<br />\n當你用支付寶和淘寶每日豪過光棍節時想想別人，那些還未接近西九已經被定暴動罪的人。<br />\n<br />\n當你想到那些近在身邊忽然被DQ的人，想想你自己，然後說：<br />\n<br />\n我希望自己是黑暗中的蠟燭、莫須有罪名前的敲鐘人、抗爭路上苦行者的補給站、將雙重煽惑又煽惑化為棟篤笑的人。&mdash;&mdash;改寫曹疏影翻譯巴勒斯坦詩人穆罕默德．達維什的「想想別人」，獻給佔中九子與同道人。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「佔中」教父 (尊子)"}]}